title: Comix Book # 1-5
description:
Marvel Comics attempted to publish underground comics in 1975 which resulted in Comix Book # 1-3

# 4 and 5 were published by Kitchen Sink

Now obviously, a mainstream publisher would never get close to material similar to, say, Joe Blow, but still quite a few notable creators contributed

Odd cases these books are, but they contain some great stuff

Including:
Skip Williamson, Kim Deitch, Trina Robbins, Justing Green, Howard Cruse, Basil Wolverton, Mike Ploog, Harvey Pekar, Kelly Freas, Bill Griffith, Scott Shaw, Gary Hallgren, Art Spiegelman, Denis Kitchen, Steve Stiles, John Pound, Joel Beck, Willy Murphy, Leslie Cabarga, Sharon Rudahl and others
